{"id":3008,"date":"2025-06-05T13:39:27","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:39:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=3008"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:20:12","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:20:12","slug":"cham-soc-da-mun-dung-cach","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/cham-soc-da-mun-dung-cach\/","title":{"rendered":"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch: Quy tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n chuy\u00ean gia"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ef1 ti, lo l\u1eafng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c <\/span><\/i><b><i>ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft skincare d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da m\u1ee5n qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-mun-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Da m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ee5n l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da b\u1ecb vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m do c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n b\u00ean trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ho\u1eb7c m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t, c\u1ed5, l\u01b0ng,&#8230; Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 do l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc b\u1edfi d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5. \u0110\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"quy-trinh-cham-soc-da-mun-dung-cach-ban-ngay-va-ban-dem\"><\/span><b>Quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch: Ban ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 ban \u0111\u00eam<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf vi\u1ec7c r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t quy tr\u00ecnh khoa h\u1ecdc, \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n s\u00e1ng \u2013 t\u1ed1i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n tham kh\u1ea3o.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3738\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3738\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3738\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-Thumb.webp\" alt=\"ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-Thumb.webp 1200w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-Thumb-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-Thumb-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-Thumb-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-Thumb-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3738\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoi-sang-quy-trinh-cham-soc-da-mun-ban-ngay\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng: Quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n ban ng\u00e0y<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. V\u1edbi da m\u1ee5n, h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH t\u1eeb 5.0 &#8211; 6.5, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. Vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: D\u00f9ng toner c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t, da th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. Toner s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da v\u00e0 se kh\u00edt l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. N\u00ean tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i toner ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t hoa c\u00fac ho\u1eb7c rau m\u00e1.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3739\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3739\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3739\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-1.webp\" alt=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n ban ng\u00e0y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3739\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n ban ng\u00e0y<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Thoa serum \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Serum l\u00e0 &#8220;tr\u1ee3 th\u1ee7&#8221; \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gom c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam v\u00e0 m\u1edd th\u00e2m. H\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn serum ch\u1ee9a Glycolic acid, tinh d\u1ea7u tr\u00e0m tr\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c c\u00e2y ph\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m cho da m\u1ee5n<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ee5n v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u \u2013 n\u01b0\u1edbc. Vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu \u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u h\u01a1n, l\u00e0m m\u1ee5n n\u1eb7ng th\u00eam. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng d\u1ea1ng gel, m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u kho\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1eb1ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9 tr\u1eddi m\u01b0a hay n\u1eafng, kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 &#8220;v\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ly th\u00e2n&#8221; gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u01b0\u1edbc tia UV v\u00e0 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i. Ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng (SPF 30 tr\u1edf l\u00ean), k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u1ebft d\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da m\u00e0 v\u1eabn tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cham-soc-da-mun-dung-cach-vao-ban-dem\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u00e0o ban \u0111\u00eam<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ban \u0111\u00eam l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o. Vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u00e0o ban \u0111\u00eam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: T\u1ea9y trang k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea7m t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea9y trang l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu, ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 thoa kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng hay trang \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eb9. Vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea9y trang s\u1ebd gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1edbp b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m t\u00edch t\u1ee5 s\u00e2u trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh g\u00e2y ra m\u1ee5n. V\u1edbi l\u00e0n da m\u1ee5n, h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea9y trang d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea9y trang, d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng d\u00e0nh cho da m\u1ee5n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u h\u01a1n, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i. N\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH trung t\u00ednh (5.0 &#8211; 6.5) v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 tr\u00e0m tr\u00e0 hay BHA \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3740\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3740\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3740\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-2-2.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u00e0o ban \u0111\u00eam\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-2-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-2-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-2-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-2-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3740\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u00e0o ban \u0111\u00eam<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: X\u00f4ng h\u01a1i da m\u1eb7t<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">X\u00f4ng h\u01a1i l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u00fap l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng gi\u00e3n n\u1edf, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ea9y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n l\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea5m pha th\u00eam v\u00e0i gi\u1ecdt tinh d\u1ea7u tr\u00e0m tr\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c s\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n. Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 1-2 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y tu\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n m\u00e1u, gi\u00fap da h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft 1-2 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp da ch\u1ebft, th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh. Ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc ch\u1ee9a AHA\/BHA ho\u1eb7c enzyme tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y thay v\u00ec d\u1ea1ng h\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0n da m\u1ee5n nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da v\u1edbi toner<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, toner l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da m\u1ee5n, n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn toner c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 rau m\u00e1, hoa c\u00fac hay tr\u00e0 xanh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 6: \u0110\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gi\u00fap b\u1ed5 sung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m t\u1ee9c th\u00ec cho da. V\u1edbi da m\u1ee5n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ea5t s\u00e9t ho\u1eb7c than ho\u1ea1t t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00fat b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 se kh\u00edt l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. Ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m da b\u1ecb \u201cqu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 7: B\u00f4i tinh ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tinh ch\u1ea5t (serum) ch\u1ee9a BHA, AHA, Niacinamide hay tinh d\u1ea7u tr\u00e0m tr\u00e0 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, \u0111\u1ea9y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t. H\u00e3y thoa l\u00ean v\u00f9ng m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0i ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n sang b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 8: D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m<\/span><\/i><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f3a l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c l\u1edbp d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. D\u00f9 da m\u1ee5n c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, d\u1ea1ng gel ho\u1eb7c lotion c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 Hyaluronic Acid hay Ceramide \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eeba c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u1eeba gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhung-sai-lam-can-tranh-khi-cham-soc-da-mun\"><\/span><b>Nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen sai l\u1ea7m d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3741\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3741\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3741 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-3-2.webp\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n\" width=\"800\" height=\"481\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-3-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-3-2-300x180.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-3-2-768x462.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/27-3-2-600x361.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3741\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n: G\u00e2y vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m, s\u1eb9o th\u00e2m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u: Khi\u1ebfn da m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, k\u00edch th\u00edch ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ea1m tay l\u00ean m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean: B\u00e0n tay ch\u1ee9a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi khu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n l\u00e2y lan.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ecf qua b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea9y trang: L\u1edbp b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng chung \u0111\u1ed3 trang \u0111i\u1ec3m: T\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi khu\u1ea9n l\u00e2y lan, l\u00e0m m\u1ee5n kh\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ee9c th\u00ec, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, l\u00e0n da s\u1ebd d\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. H\u00e3y l\u1eafng nghe l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c khoa h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c th\u00f3i quen x\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n s\u1edbm c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0n da s\u1ea1ch m\u1ee5n, s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe kho\u1eafn!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft skincare d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da m\u1ee5n qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3738,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3008","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3008","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3008"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3008\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3983,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3008\/revisions\/3983"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3738"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3008"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3008"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3008"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}